chat.web.bean

Class ChatBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • chat.web.bean.ChatBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Named(value="chatBean")
 @ViewScoped
public class ChatBean
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This managed bean supports the operations and UI components of the chat page.

      • uploadVideo

        public void uploadVideo()
        This method creates a video messenger containing the Part object and invokes the saveToFileSystem method of the video handler for processing of the upload. The messenger contains a callback method to propagate the video message.
